'''伊万帕太阳能发电设施'''是一个在加州[[莫哈韦沙漠|莫哈韦沙漠]]的[[太阳热能|太阳热能]]工程，距离[[拉斯维加斯|拉斯维加斯]]市西南40英里（64 公里），规划总容量392兆瓦（MW）。<ref name=woody/>它部署了173,500 个{{link-en|定日镜|heliostat}}聚焦太阳光在位于中央的太阳能发电塔锅炉塔，每个{{link-en|定日镜|}}有两个反射镜。<ref name=woody>{{cite web |url= http://ivanpahsolar.com/ |title= Brightsource Ivanpah |access-date= 2014-04-11 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130111010740/http://ivanpahsolar.com/ |archive-date= 2013-01-11 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>该项目的1号机组是在2013年9月的初始同步测试后并入电网发电。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.businesswire.com/multimedia/home/20130924005388/en/ |title=Business Wire: Ivanpah Solar Electric Generating System Reaches ‘First Sync’ Milestone |accessdate=2014-04-11 |archive-date=2014-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141226070345/http://www.businesswire.com/multimedia/home/20130924005388/en |dead-url=no }}</ref>该设施正式开业于2014年2月13日，<ref name="AP"/>并且，它是目前世界上最大的太阳能热电站。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://spectrum.ieee.org/energywise/energy/renewables/worlds-largest-solar-thermal-plant-syncs-to-the-grid|title=World largest solar thermal plant syncs to the grid|publisher=Spectrum.ieee.org|accessdate=28 November 2014|archive-date=2020-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927142436/https://spectrum.ieee.org/energywise/energy/renewables/worlds-largest-solar-thermal-plant-syncs-to-the-grid|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://investors.nrg.com/phoenix.zhtml?c=121544&p=irol-newsArticle&ID=1899656&highlight "World's Largest Solar Thermal Power Project at Ivanpah Achieves Commercial Operation"] {{Wayback|url=http://investors.nrg.com/phoenix.zhtml?c=121544&p=irol-newsArticle&ID=1899656&highlight |date=20160129072528 }}, NRG press release, February 13, 2014.</ref>


