== 描述 ==
[[File:Ivanpah_SEGS_(1).JPG|thumb]]
[[Image:Ivanpah_SEGS_(2).JPG|thumb]]
[[File:IvanpahRunning.JPG|thumb]]拍摄。]]

伊万帕太阳能发电系统的3个太阳能热发电厂占地面积为4000英亩（1,600公顷）的公有土地，它的位置靠近[[美国西南部|美国西南部]][[莫哈韦沙漠|莫哈韦沙漠]]的加州-内华达的边界。<ref name=walsh2013>{{cite news |title=Tower of Power |last=Walsh |first=Bryan |url= |periodical=[[Time_(magazine)|Time (magazine)]] |date=24 June 2013 |type=paper |pages=Business 1–4 }}</ref>附近是[[15号州际公路|15号州际公路]]和加利福尼亚州{{link-en|加州伊万帕|Ivanpah, California|伊万帕}}的北部。<ref name="CEC-brief">{{cite web |url=http://www.energy.ca.gov/sitingcases/ivanpah/documents/2010-04-01_Energy_Commission_Staff_Opening_Brief.pdf |title=Docket No. 07-AFC-5: Energy Commission Staff's Opening Brief |format=PDF |date=1 April 2010 |publisher=[[California_Energy_Commission|California Energy Commission]] |accessdate=15 April |archive-date=2010-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101008235531/http://www.energy.ca.gov/sitingcases/ivanpah/documents/2010-04-01_Energy_Commission_Staff_Opening_Brief.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>从附近的{{link-en|莫哈韦国家保护区|Mojave National Preserve}}和{{link-en|州立野地保护区|Stateline Wilderness}}都可以观看到这个地点。<ref name="CEC-brief"/>

该设施由定日镜场把太阳光聚焦在位于中央的太阳能发电塔接收器。接收器产生蒸汽来驱动特别改装的[[蒸汽渦輪發動機|蒸汽涡轮发电机]]。对于第一个发电厂，订购了最大的完全以太阳能为动力的蒸汽涡轮发电机组，使用的是{{convert|123|MW|-3|adj=on}} [[西门子|西门子]]公司的SST-900单壳体再加热涡轮机。<ref>[[Siemens|Siemens]] press release [http://www.siemens.com/press/en/pressrelease/?press=/en/pressrelease/2008/oil_gas/eog200812013.htm Siemens to supply 123 MW steam turbine-generator set for solar thermal power plant in California] {{Wayback|url=http://www.siemens.com/press/en/pressrelease/?press=%2Fen%2Fpressrelease%2F2008%2Foil_gas%2Feog200812013.htm |date=20171213201004 }}</ref>除了蒸汽涡轮发电机之外，西门子公司提供仪表和控制系统。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usa.siemens.com/energy-efficiency/energy-efficiency.html|title=Energy efficiency. Rethinking the energy system here in the U.S.|author=Siemens|publisher=Usa.siemens.com|accessdate=28 November 2014|archive-date=2013-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130511222228/http://www.usa.siemens.com/energy-efficiency/energy-efficiency.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2010年10月取得了最终审批。<ref>[http://www.businessgreen.com/business-green/news/2271240/brightsource-secures-final BrightSource secures final approval for Ivanpah solar project] {{Wayback|url=http://www.businessgreen.com/business-green/news/2271240/brightsource-secures-final |date=20101011034658 }}, BusinessGreen.com staff, BusinessGreen, 08 Oct 2010</ref>在2010年10月27日，该项目在加州州长[[阿诺德·施瓦辛格|阿诺德·施瓦辛格]]，内政部长[[肯·薩拉查|肯·薩拉查]]和其他政要聚集主持下在[[莫哈韦沙漠|莫哈韦沙漠]]正式破土动工。<ref name=woody/>因为建造它的决定位于生态完好的沙漠[[栖息地|栖息地]]，该项目产生了争议。<ref>{{cite news|last=Lewis|first=Judith|title=As the climate warms, environmentalists square off over Big Solar's claim to the Mojave Desert|url=http://www.hcn.org/issues/41.8/high-noon/article_view?b_start:int=0&-C=|accessdate=3 December 2011|newspaper=High Country News|date=4 May 2009|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120406092450/http://www.hcn.org/issues/41.8/high-noon/article_view?b_start:int=0&-C=|archivedate=2012年4月6日}}</ref>

== 奖项 ==
